Put this folder in your home directory
then open the directory in your terminal by using "cd bin" 
then from there you need to give executive permissions to my files by using "chmod +x crucified.sh mambo.sh mambomas.sh operao.sh rick.sh tom.sh umapyoi.sh umarap.sh"
then it should work!

A YT Guide by me to help with the install and such :) https://youtu.be/PXDsvdUBSnA

